磷脂酸可在磷脂水解酶（LPPs）催化下被降解为二酰甘油，<ref name="pmid8681429">{{cite journal en|author=Brindley DN, Waggoner DW |title=Phosphatidate phosphohydrolase and signal transduction |journal=Chem. Phys. Lipids |volume=80 |issue=1-2 |pages=45–57 |pmid=8681429 |doi= 10.1016/0009-3084(96)02545-5|url=|date=May 1996}}</ref><ref name="pmid9733709">{{cite journal en |author=Brindley DN, Waggoner DW |title=Mammalian lipid phosphate phosphohydrolases |journal=J. Biol. Chem. |volume=273 |issue=38 |pages=24281–4 |pmid=9733709 |doi=10.1074/jbc.273.38.24281 |url=http://www.jbc.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=9733709 |date=September 1998 |access-date=2010-01-02 |archive-date=2019-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190924225314/http://www.jbc.org/content/273/38/24281.long |dead-url=no }}</ref>也可在[[磷脂酶A|磷脂酶A]]（PLA）催化下降解为溶血磷脂酸。

==在细胞中的功能==
磷脂酸在细胞中的角色主要如下：
* 作为其他脂类的合成前体。
* 借助其物理性质影响膜曲率。
* 充当信号脂类分子。<ref name="pmid15310762">{{cite journal en|author=Delon C, Manifava M, Wood E, ''et al.'' |title=Sphingosine kinase 1 is an intracellular effector of phosphatidic acid |journal=J. Biol. Chem. |volume=279 |issue=43 |pages=44763–74 |pmid=15310762 |doi=10.1074/jbc.M405771200 |url=|date=October 2004}}</ref>

